 class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/WP/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.WPMonad\">WPMonad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">Pred</span> <span class=\"fn\">EPred</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Init/While.html#Lean.Loop\">Lean.Loop</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">β</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#ForInStep\">ForInStep</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></span></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">measure</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.RepeatVariant\">RepeatVariant</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">inv</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.RepeatInvariant\">RepeatInvariant</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span> <span class=\"fn\">Pred</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">einv</span> : <span class=\"fn\">EPred</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">step</span> :\n  <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>),\n    <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦃</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">inv</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inl\">Sum.inl</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦄</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit.unit\">(</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit.unit\">)</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦃</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#ForInStep\">ForInStep</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>) =&gt;\n      <span class=\"fn\">match <span class=\"fn\">r</span> with\n      | <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#ForInStep.yield\">ForInStep.yield</a> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span></span> =&gt;\n        <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.meet\">Lean.Order.meet</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.ofProp\">Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.ofProp</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">measure</span> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">measure</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span>))</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">inv</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inl\">Sum.inl</a> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span>)</span>)</span></span>\n      | <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#ForInStep.done\">ForInStep.done</a> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span></span> =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">inv</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inr\">Sum.inr</a> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span>)</span></span></span></span><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">;</a>       <span class=\"fn\">einv</span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦄</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦃</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">inv</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inl\">Sum.inl</a> <span class=\"fn\">init</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦄</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#ForIn.forIn\">forIn</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span> <span class=\"fn\">init</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦃</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">inv</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inr\">Sum.inr</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span>)</span></span></span><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">;</a> <span class=\"fn\">einv</span> <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/Basic.html#Std.Internal.Do.Triple\">⦄</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Specification for `forIn` over a `Lean.Loop`. The cursor is `β ⊕ β`: `.inl b` means\n\"still iterating with `b`\", `.inr b` means \"finished with result `b`\".\n","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.Spec.forIn_loop","kind":"theorem","line":2498,"name":"Std.Internal.Do.Spec.forIn_loop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.lean#L2498-L2532"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">noncomputable abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.RepeatInvariant.ofInvariantAndBreak\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">RepeatInvariant</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofInvariantAndBreak</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α </span><span class=\"fn\">Pred</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Assertion.html#Std.Internal.Do.Assertion\">Assertion</a> <span class=\"fn\">Pred</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">inv </span><span class=\"fn\">onBreak</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">Pred</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.RepeatInvariant\">RepeatInvariant</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">Pred</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Construct an invariant from a loop invariant `inv` and a break condition `onBreak`.\n\n`inv` holds at the end of every loop iteration (including the breaking one), and `onBreak` holds in\naddition to `inv` once the loop is done. For a normal `while` loop `onBreak` can be taken as the\nnegation of the loop condition.\n","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.RepeatInvariant.ofInvariantAndBreak","kind":"def","line":2484,"name":"Std.Internal.Do.RepeatInvariant.ofInvariantAndBreak","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.lean#L2484-L2495"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Triple/SpecLemmas.html#Std.Internal.Do.Spec.repeatM\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Spec</span>.<span class=